data.title: Norman Anthony “Norm” Duberville (1898
data.meta_description: United States Marine Corps Veteran of WWI.  Fought at the Battle of Belleau Wood and was awarded the Silver Star.  The following is his citation:  Norman A. Duberville AWARDS BY DATE OF ACTION: 1 of 1  Silver Star Citation AWARDED FOR ACTIONS DURING World War I Service: Marine Corps Rank: Private Division: 2d Division,...
